---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
import CTABanner from '../components/CTABanner.astro';
import JsonLd from '../components/JsonLd.astro';
import { PHONE, PHONE_RAW, SITE_URL } from '../consts';

const title = 'Celebration of Life Planning | Raleigh NC';
const description = 'Plan a celebration of life that truly honors your loved one. Learn how pre-need insurance covers every detail of a personalized memorial service in Raleigh NC.';

const serviceJsonLd = {
	'@context': 'https://schema.org',
	'@type': 'Service',
	name: 'Celebration of Life Planning',
	description: 'Personalized celebration of life planning and pre-need insurance coverage in Raleigh and Wake County, NC.',
	provider: {
		'@type': 'InsuranceAgency',
		name: 'Cutlip Associates, LLC',
		url: SITE_URL,
	},
	areaServed: {
		'@type': 'City',
		name: 'Raleigh',
		containedInPlace: { '@type': 'State', name: 'North Carolina' },
	},
};
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} keywords="celebration of life, personalized memorial service, funeral alternatives Raleigh NC">
	<Hero variant="interior" title="A Celebration as Unique as the Life It Honors" subtitle="More families are choosing celebrations of life — services that focus on who someone was, not just that they're gone." />

	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
		<Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'Celebration of Life' }]} />

		<!-- What Is a Celebration of Life? -->
		<section class="mb-16">
			<SectionHeading title="What Is a Celebration of Life?" accent />
			<div class="space-y-4 text-charcoal-700">
				<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
					A celebration of life is a memorial service that focuses on honoring and remembering the person who has passed — their personality, passions, achievements, and the joy they brought to others.
				</p>
				<p class="leading-relaxed">
					Unlike a traditional funeral, which follows a more structured format, a celebration of life can take any form. It can be held anywhere — a park, a restaurant, a family home, a church, or a funeral home chapel. The tone is often uplifting, with laughter and shared stories alongside tears and reflection.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-border-light">
					<h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-3">Traditional Funeral</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-charcoal-500 text-sm">
						<li>Formal, structured service</li>
						<li>Typically held within days of passing</li>
						<li>Usually at a funeral home or church</li>
						<li>Focuses on mourning and religious ceremony</li>
						<li>Body or casket often present</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-linen rounded-xl p-6 border border-border-light">
					<h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-3">Celebration of Life</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-charcoal-500 text-sm">
						<li>Flexible, personalized format</li>
						<li>Can be held weeks or months later</li>
						<li>Any meaningful venue</li>
						<li>Focuses on the person's life and legacy</li>
						<li>May include cremation urn, photos, or memorabilia</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- How to Personalize -->
		<section class="mb-16">
			<SectionHeading title="How to Personalize a Celebration of Life" accent />
			<p class="text-charcoal-500 mb-8">Every life is different — and every celebration should be too. Here are ways families personalize their services:</p>
			<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
				{[
					{ title: 'Venue', desc: 'A favorite restaurant, a park by the lake, the family backyard, or a beautiful chapel. The location sets the tone.' },
					{ title: 'Music', desc: 'From gospel hymns to jazz to their favorite playlist — music brings the room together and captures who they were.' },
					{ title: 'Photo & Video Tributes', desc: 'Slideshows, photo boards, or video montages that walk through a life well-lived — childhood, family, milestones.' },
					{ title: 'Themes & Hobbies', desc: 'A fishing theme, military honors, gardening motifs, or their favorite sports team colors. It\'s all fair game.' },
					{ title: 'Food & Gathering', desc: 'Their famous recipe served at the reception, a barbecue cookout, or a formal dinner. Sharing a meal brings people together.' },
					{ title: 'Readings & Stories', desc: 'Family members share memories, read favorite poems, or tell the stories that made everyone laugh.' },
					{ title: 'Legacy Projects', desc: 'Charitable donations, memory books for guests to sign, or planting a tree in their honor.' },
					{ title: 'Release & Remembrance', desc: 'Butterfly releases, lantern ceremonies, or a final toast — meaningful moments that bring closure.' },
				].map((item) => (
					<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-border-light">
						<h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
						<p class="text-charcoal-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
					</div>
				))}
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- How Pre-Need Insurance Covers It -->
		<section class="mb-16">
			<SectionHeading title="How Pre-Need Insurance Covers Every Detail" accent />
			<div class="space-y-4 text-charcoal-700">
				<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
					Many families worry that a celebration of life is "extra" — something outside the scope of a funeral plan. The truth is, your pre-need insurance can cover every element of a celebration of life, just as it would a traditional funeral.
				</p>
				<p class="leading-relaxed">
					When you plan ahead with Duane, you'll document exactly what kind of service you want. If that's a celebration of life at your favorite park with your favorite music, that's what your family will know to do — and the costs are covered.
				</p>
				<div class="bg-linen rounded-xl p-8 border border-border-light mt-6">
					<h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-charcoal-900 text-lg mb-4">Your pre-need plan can include:</h3>
					<ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
						{[
							'Venue rental and setup',
							'Catering and refreshments',
							'Flowers and decorations',
							'Photo and video production',
							'Music — live or recorded',
							'Printed programs and keepsakes',
							'Cremation or burial costs',
							'Transportation and coordination',
						].map((item) => (
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-charcoal-700">
								<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
								</svg>
								<span>{item}</span>
							</li>
						))}
					</ul>
				</div>
				<p class="leading-relaxed mt-6">
					The best part? You get to plan your own celebration. Choose the music, the venue, the food, and the stories you want told. Your family will have a clear roadmap and the financial resources to make it happen exactly as you envisioned.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>

	<CTABanner title="Plan a Celebration That Reflects Your Life" subtitle="Call Duane to start planning a celebration of life that's uniquely yours — at today's prices." />

	<JsonLd data={serviceJsonLd} />
</BaseLayout>
